title: Family Guy: The Complete Griffin Family Tree

media:group.media:title: Family Guy: The Complete Griffin Family Tree
media:group.media:description:
In this video we look at the complete family tree of Peter Griffin from Family Guy. Voiced by Seth Macfarlane, we look at Peter's entire family history. Taking a look at the Family Guy cutaways, as well as the full Family Guy episodes, I've put charted Peter's family tree from season 1 to newest Family Guy season.

We also look at the funniest Family Guy moments from Peter, Lois, Chris, Meg and Brian. As well as other Family Guy characters from Quahog Rhode Island.
